---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
JMX Endpoints
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- by default all endpoints are exposed
- not all are enabled (i.e. /shutdown)

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Enable/Disable enpoints
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
management.endpoints.jmx.exposure.include=*
management.endpoints.jmx.exposure.exclude=*

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Try It!
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
JConsole comes with Java!

- start app (ActuatorCustomEndpointsApplication)
- open terminal and run: jconsole
- select app (ActuatorCustomEndpointsApplication)

- select MBeans tab
- Expand the org.springframework.boot package and the Endpoint
- all endpoints, including custom ones are there
- Expand Todostats>Operations
- execute commands